'''Tay Peng Hian''' [[Fellow of the Royal Philatelic Society London|FRPSL]] is a Singaporean [[philatelist]] who was appointed to the [[Roll of Distinguished Philatelists]] in 1996. He is a fellow of the [[Royal Philatelic Society London]]. Hian is a specialist in the philately of Burma and the Straits Settlements.<ref name=roll1996>"The Roll of Distinguished Philatelists", ''[[The London Philatelist]]'', Vol. 105, No. 1235 (May 1996), pp. 103-104.</ref>
